_sText: This map was originally made for CS 1.6. I recreated this map for Source from the 1.6 version that Boomstick made. This is not perfect so please post any improvments, helpful criticism (no matter how harsh), or suggest ideas. I am looking forward to upgrading this map as soon as I hear any constructive feedback from you guys. Note: My graphics card isn't that great so the graphics and the props will look better in-game. Have fun playing it! EDIT: I added the skybox textures to the archive, I forgot to add it the first time sorry.
